                &lt;a href=&#34;https://srikanthperinkulam.com/2021/01/01/covelong-riders/images/20210102_040253-scaled.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./images/20210102_040253-scaled.jpg&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; alt=&#34;20210102_040253-scaled.jpg&#34; /&gt;&lt;a&gt;
